Coach Tian.

45
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,320
Guoduo.

46
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,300
Take a 10-minute break.

47
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,620
Why haven't you come recently?

48
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:06,360
I heard from Lingling

49
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,180
