50
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,800
Yes.

51
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:12,420
But the school is investigating.

52
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,960
Coach Tian.

53
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:16,260
I came to tell you.

54
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,760
Thank you for your help

55
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,220
during this time.

56
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,380
I've thought it over.

57
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,540
I still want to go back to Xingang to play.

58
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,260
I guessed you were going to tell me this.

59
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,900
But I still hope you will reconsider.

60
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,080
Though I haven't been your coach

61
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,160
for long,

62
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,680
you can feel your improvement,

63
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,660
right?

64
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,620
No matter where you train,

65
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,780
I hope you'll set standards for yourself

66
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,460
in terms of time and quality.

67
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,780
I will train hard.

68
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,680
But I've already decided.

69
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,420
I want to play with Chen Weilan.

70
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,700
You can ask her to come play here too.

71
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,140
Thank you for your kindness, Coach.

72
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,520
After all, I study in Xingang.

73
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,360
My teammates and I built

74
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,220
the Xingang beach volleyball team.

75
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,940
I still want to be with them.

76
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,720
Since you've made up your mind,

77
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,020
I respect your decision.

78
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,740
Thank you for your understanding.

79
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,480
Then I'll go now.

80
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,600
I won't disturb you anymore.

81
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,440
Go ahead.

82
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,280
Duoduo.

83
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,960
Coach.

84
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,340
Are you really planning to leave?

85
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,140
Not staying to train with us?

86
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,260
It's okay.

87
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,880
We're not in the same school,

88
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,220
but we can still play together.

89
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,680
Wait a moment.

90
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,200
Coach.

91
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:37,080
Can I have a word with Duoduo?

92
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:37,920
Ten minutes.

93
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,060
Okay, thank you.

94
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,140
Let's talk over there.

95
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,040
Duoduo.

96
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:47,620
Why are you still thinking
of partnering with Chen?

97
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,560
The two of you are

98
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,820
on different levels.

99
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,320
When you're with her,

100
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,760
others can't see your strengths.

101
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,460
They'll only say you're holding her back.

102
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,760
Stay and train with us.

103
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,600
Isn't that good?

104
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,960
I can't abandon her

105
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,940
and come here to escape

106
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,180
from my problem

107
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,620
just because she and I

108
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,180
have a big skill gap.

109
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,900
It's precisely because of the gap

110
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,180
that makes me see more clearly

111
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,880
how far I am

112
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,340
from becoming an excellent athlete.

113
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,840
So, I'm more motivated

114
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,060
to work hard to catch up.

115
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,540
That's what I should do now.

116
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:26,880
(Ocean University)

117
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,380
Stop being stubborn.

118
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,820
You've partnered with her for so long.

119
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,400
Her playing style

120
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,740
doesn't suit you at all.

121
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,320
And she's going to Beijing soon.

122
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,240
Are you going to chase her to Beijing?

123
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,540
No one's going to Beijing.

124
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,500
I'm staying in Xingang

125
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,440
and continuing to partner with her.

126
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,460
It's because you didn't make it into the NYT

127
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,860
so you're staying here, right?

128
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,120
If you had the chance,

129
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,260
you would've left long ago.

130
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,520
I'm not like some people,

131
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,560
who gave up their partner

132
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,100
for their own sake.

133
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,760
You're keeping Li Guoduo at Ocean Uni

134
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,480
because of Shao Nian, right?

135
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,020
How many times do I have to say it?

136
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,230
I like Shao Nian, so what?

137
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,600
Everyone knows

138
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,060
I like Shao Nian.

139
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,840
I want to keep Duoduo

140
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,160
training at Ocean Uni.

141
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,980
These two things aren't contradictory.

142
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,620
Besides, Duoduo just said

143
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,400
since coming to Ocean Uni,

144
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,620
her progress has been great.

145
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,040
Everything I've done

146
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,080
is for her good.

147
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:34,940
Enough.

148
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,360
Lingling.

149
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,720
I just told Coach Tian

150
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,940
very clearly.

151
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,280
I want to go back

152
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,500
and play with them.

153
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,220
I'll continue playing with Chen Weilan.

154
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,440
- Let's go.
- You're not helping me

155
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,280
with Shao Nian?

156
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,520
Tu Lingling.

157
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,140
Liking Shao Nian is your business.

158
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:07,260
It has nothing to do with me.

159
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,680
You mentioned it,

160
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,860
so I'll make it clear.

161
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,280
If Shao Nian tells me himself

162
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,300
that he likes you.

163
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,720
Then I bless you

164
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,780
and congratulate you.

165
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,360
I hope you can compete

166
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,780
for him fairly and justly with me.

167
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,240
If you keep scheming

168
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,340
behind my back,

169
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,700
I won't accept it.

170
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:35,560
You finally admit you like him.

171
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,400
Yes.

172
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:37,900
I like him.

173
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,800
There's nothing wrong with that.

174
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,500
Alright, stop talking. You can go now.

175
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,100
As for whom he chooses,

176
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,300
that's not for us to decide.

177
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:25,260
(Yuanxiong)

178
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,640
Jingxuan, thanks for this computer.

179
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,130
- It helped me a lot.
- My pleasure.

180
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,420
It's nothing.

181
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,640
But why did you suddenly want to watch

182
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,860
the video of Xiaojing's match
against Ocean Uni?

183
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:43,030
Gao Ge insisted that I go

184
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,600
to the library with him this afternoon

185
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,840
to look up some materials

186
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,060
and review the game.

187
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:51,180
Weilan, look. How does this dress look on me?

188
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,720
It looks good.

189
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,900
You didn't even look.

190
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,380
It is good.

191
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,020
How about this one?

192
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,020
What's the difference?

193
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,860
Completely different.

194
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,400
They're both white.

195
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,220
The styles are different.

196
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,100
You look good in both.

197
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,980
You have quite a lot of dresses.

198
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,800
Not really.

199
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,240
I'm always worried about not having

200
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,380
enough clothes.

201
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,720
You change clothes every day.

202
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,100
And you're worried about that?

203
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,100
Weilan.

204
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,280
I don't think I've ever seen you

205
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,620
wearing a dress.

206
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,440
You're always wearing

207
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,980
the same thing.

208
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,980
I think you could change it.

209
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:39,020
I won't change. This is convenient.

210
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,580
Look at this one. How about it?

211
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:54,100
I think it should suit you.

212
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,920
Here's this one back.

213
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:07,860
Okay.

214
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,620
What are you photographing?

215
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,960
Gao Ge.

216
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,200
What's up? Let's go.

217
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,080
You...

218
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,880
Why are you dressed like that?

219
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:26,780
What took you so long? Hurry up.

220
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:28,780
Wait a moment.

221
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,980
The air conditioning is strong.

222
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,960
- No need.
- Put this on.

223
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,880
No need.

224
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,140
Put it on.

225
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,620
Chen Weilan.

226
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,620
Chen Weilan.

227
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:00,820
Yesterday,

228
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,860
I watched Xue Chen's match video.

229
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,020
I found she is a bit like you.

230
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:07,240
So today I came here to see

231
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,740
if there are any of her materials.

232
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,960
Okay.

233
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:15,260
Her shoulder joint was also injured.

234
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,120
Very similar to yours.

235
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,400
But it didn't stop her

236
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,400
from becoming the top

237
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,540
beach volleyball player.

238
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,220
So?

239
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:24,760
So...

240
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,140
So, as long as

241
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:28,600
you can overcome difficulties,

242
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,160
injuries don't matter,

243
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,300
You can still play well.

244
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:33,760
Thank you.

245
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,580
I have one more thing.

246
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,580
You look good

247
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,660
in this outfit today.

248
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,060
But

249
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,280
when I'm not around,

250
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,900
can you not wear this one?

251
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,140
Why?

252
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,780
I'm a bit worried.

253
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:09,240
What's there to worry about?

254
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,940
I can take care of myself.

255
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,000
Come in.

256
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,620
Jingxuan.

257
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,080
I'm returning your dress.

258
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,020
Did you wear it?

259
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,180
I did.

260
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,880
Did Gao Ge see it?

261
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:36,940
What did he say?

262
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,520
He said your dress looks good.

263
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:41,920
He can't just say the dress looks good.

264
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,800
He meant

265
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,640
you're beautiful, making the dress look good.

266
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,740
But today, wearing this dress outside,

267
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,440
I was secretly photographed.

268
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,460
Secretly photographed?

269
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:55,160
Maybe someone who studies photography?

270
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,500
Thought you were a model.

271
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:58,120
Doesn't seem like it.

272
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,980
Gao Ge even shouted at him.

273
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,140
I'll head back now.

274
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,320
Bye-bye.

275
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,280
Bye-bye.

276
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,560
Does her family depend

277
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,140
on the restaurant for a living?

278
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,260
Yes, so what?

279
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:40,480
Their restaurant

280
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,980
is quite famous here.

281
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,880
Did I raise you

282
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,160
and send you to college

283
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,480
so you could do these

284
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,420
tiring jobs for them?

285
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:48,280
What's wrong

286
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,240
with being

287
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,460
with the person I like?

288
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:51,480
The person you like

289
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,800
may not want to be with you.

290
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,780
Impossible.

291
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,280
No need to tell me

292
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,640
about it anymore.

293
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,900
I have just two words:

294
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,080
I disagree.

295
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,400
I have three words:

296
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,320
I don't care.

297
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,780
Lingling is a very outstanding girl.

298
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,700
You should get to know her better.

299
00:14:06,920 --> 00:14:08,000
Do you really want

300
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,180
me to get to know her?

301
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,020
Yes.

302
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,360
She's beautiful

303
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,480
and a good player.

304
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:15,160
So, I'm also going to Ocean University

305
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,340
as a non-roster player.

306
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,180
Professor.

307
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,260
It's you.

308
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,540
Here to see Shao Nian?

309
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,260
You remember me?

310
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,620
Is Shao Nian here?

311
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,820
No. He doesn't have class today.

312
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:47,220
