313
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,400
Yes.

314
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:50,420
His mother arranged for him to intern,

315
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,120
so it's hard to see him.

316
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,020
He's

317
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,160
very smart,

318
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:56,460
