319
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,680
But

320
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,900
I think

321
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,400
as his girlfriend,

322
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,780
you should advise him well.

323
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:05,680
Doing all sorts of things now

324
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:06,980
