325
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,020
I understand.

326
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,260
Thank you, Professor.

327
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:39,860
Mom,

328
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,860
