330
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,020
Why don't you try to understand me?

331
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:56,220
You are our only heir.

332
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,780
The company's future

333
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,260
