334
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:01,500
You have to inherit it.

335
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:09,780
Can I go back to the BBQ shop one more time?

336
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,980
Why?

337
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,220
Sweetie,

338
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,020
can you promise me

339
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:21,220
to intern at the hospital?

340
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,460
I promise you,

341
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:29,020
but I want to get my luggage back.

342
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:31,640
Alright.

343
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,060
Come back early.

344
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:44,080
(Dafu BBQ)
Miss, look at this one.

345
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,440
It suits you perfectly.

346
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,460
Uncle Li.

347
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,600
Sorry.

348
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,680
There's a family issue.

349
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:51,300
I can't continue working here.

350
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:58,900
Shao Nian,

351
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:00,220
thank you

352
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:03,140
for helping us all this time.

353
00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:07,340
I think you're great in many aspects.

354
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:11,500
I like you a lot.

355
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,860
You're too kind, Uncle Li.

356
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:15,900
I really like the atmosphere here.

357
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,020
If it weren't for my issues,

358
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:18,700
I would want to earn more money here.

359
00:17:19,860 --> 00:17:21,220
Don't say that.

360
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:22,540
You're overqualified

361
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:24,180
for this job.

362
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:26,060
Uncle Li,

363
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:27,580
I'll be going now.

364
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:28,740
We'll meet again.

365
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,060
I'll transfer

366
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:33,220
your salary for this month.

367
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:34,420
You're too kind, Uncle Li.

368
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,180
I'll be going now. Bye-bye.

369
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:37,100
Bye-bye.

370
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:41,300
Did you tidy up your room?

371
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,260
Yes.

372
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:43,420
It's clean and tidy.

373
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:44,260
Don't worry.

374
00:17:44,860 --> 00:17:46,340
Good that you're responsible.

375
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:48,780
Don't be lazy,

376
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:50,260
Help your mom more.

377
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:51,300
You're so lazy.

378
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:52,660
