389
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:38,580
This is a new style.

390
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:40,940
It suits you perfectly.

391
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,220
Have a look.

392
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:45,500
There's a bargain now.

393
00:19:23,540 --> 00:19:25,380
