397
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:30,660
I'm not angry

398
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:31,980
about you mentioning it.

399
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,940
I know why you're upset.

400
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:34,500
It's because I didn't support you.

401
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:35,660
You figured that out, huh?

402
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:37,460
I've deeply reflected on my actions.

403
00:19:37,660 --> 00:19:40,140
As your good friend and mentor,

404
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:42,300
