412
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:23,700
Nurse.

413
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:24,860
Hello.

414
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:25,980
May I ask

415
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,340
where Dr. Shao is?

416
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:29,220
Dr. Shao is doing rounds over there.

417
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:31,380
Alright, I'll go find him.

418
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,620
