- No problem.

419
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:43,780
Mom.

420
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:47,620
Dr. Shao.

421
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:50,060
Though you're an intern,

422
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,380
