Hello, may I ask if Dr. Shao is here?

425
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:56,740
Dr. Shao is doing rounds over there.

426
00:20:57,100 --> 00:20:57,940
- Duoduo.
- Stop.

427
00:20:57,940 --> 00:20:58,980
When will he finish?

428
00:20:58,980 --> 00:21:00,140
Hurry and do the rounds.

429
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,500
I'm not sure.

430
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:03,300
How about you wait here for a while?

431
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:04,700
Alright.

432
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:06,900
Auntie.

433
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:10,020
How did you find this place?

434
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,020
I saw

435
00:21:13,020 --> 00:21:14,540
