436
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,100
I thought it was a pity

437
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:17,780
because they're really good.

438
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:20,020
Look, he paints so well,

439
00:21:20,020 --> 00:21:21,100
right?

440
00:21:21,100 --> 00:21:23,140
It's really a waste to throw them away.

441
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:26,700
He was just doodling out of boredom.

442
00:21:27,060 --> 00:21:28,740
He didn't take it seriously,

443
00:21:29,140 --> 00:21:30,460
and you picked them up.

444
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:33,900
I just think

445
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:35,740
he's really talented

446
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:37,740
and passionate about painting.

447
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:38,780
You think it's good.

448
00:21:38,780 --> 00:21:40,100
Does everyone else agree?

449
00:21:40,620 --> 00:21:42,460
He can't make a living from it.

450
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,380
Young lady,

451
00:21:44,820 --> 00:21:46,540
my son becoming a doctor

452
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:48,260
is his destiny.

453
00:21:48,260 --> 00:21:50,500
Don't waste his time.

454
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,640
Take these paintings and leave.

455
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:53,980
(Nurse's Station)

456
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:55,620
Auntie,

457
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:56,620
I didn't bring them here

458
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:58,460
for any other reason.

459
00:21:58,460 --> 00:21:59,500
I just think

460
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,220
Shao Nian is passionate about painting

461
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:02,740
and has been bravely

462
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:03,820
pursuing his dream.

463
00:22:03,820 --> 00:22:05,340
I hope you can support him.

464
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:06,180
I believe

465
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:07,420
he will achieve great success

466
00:22:07,420 --> 00:22:09,380
in painting.

467
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:12,060
Young lady, you're too naive

468
00:22:12,380 --> 00:22:13,620
and idealistic.

469
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:16,220
People can't fight reality.

470
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:18,540
My son is busy working.

471
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:21,500
Don't interfere with his work.

472
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:24,700
Leave now.

473
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:30,780
Alright, Auntie.

474
00:22:31,460 --> 00:22:32,300
Sorry.

475
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:55,860
Careful.

476
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:57,220
- Put it here.
- That one higher.

477
00:22:57,660 --> 00:22:58,860
