478
00:22:59,540 --> 00:23:00,860
It's fine. Put it there.

479
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:01,820
I'll put it here first.

480
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:02,700
Come, come.

481
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,780
