498
00:23:28,620 --> 00:23:29,820
- Swap these two.
- Here.

499
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:30,900
- Give me a tag.
- Right.

500
00:23:32,660 --> 00:23:34,380
- Here.
- I'll do it.

501
00:23:37,280 --> 00:23:40,820
♪Unable to escape or leave♪

502
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:45,260
