503
00:23:45,260 --> 00:23:48,580
♪Because I'm here♪

504
00:23:48,590 --> 00:23:50,180
Maybe put this one on the shelf.

505
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:51,340
Duoduo, put it on the shelf.

506
00:23:51,340 --> 00:23:52,260
There's one more here.

507
00:23:52,260 --> 00:23:53,180
- Look.
