508
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:54,020
Let me see.

509
00:23:54,980 --> 00:23:55,820
This one.

510
00:23:55,820 --> 00:23:57,700
Hang this one.

511
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,300
Hang it higher. This one's suitable.

512
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:00,940
How to do this?

513
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,260
This goes on top.

514
00:24:03,260 --> 00:24:04,300
Looks good.

515
00:24:05,870 --> 00:24:07,730
See? It aligns perfectly with your painting.

516
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,420
Do you have the tag for this one?

517
00:24:09,420 --> 00:24:10,500
Put it in the gap.

518
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:11,740
- Here, here.
- How to fix it?

519
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:13,500
Bring it here. Let me see.

520
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:14,420
Seems it's wrong.

521
00:24:14,420 --> 00:24:15,340
Why are you fixing it?

522
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:16,420
Put it in the middle first.

523
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,380
I'll fix it first, so...

524
00:24:17,380 --> 00:24:18,740
It won't be visible.

525
00:24:19,540 --> 00:24:20,580
Put it here.

526
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,860
- Put it here.
- Okay.

527
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:25,140
Everyone, come see this painting.

528
00:24:25,140 --> 00:24:27,460
This must be placed
in the most prominent position.

529
00:24:27,460 --> 00:24:29,300
- Right.
- This is our family photo.

530
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:31,700
Look. It says "About Friendship".

531
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,340
Xiaojing, here.

532
00:24:34,340 --> 00:24:35,980
Look at this. It's you, right?

533
00:24:37,260 --> 00:24:38,330
So cool.

534
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:45,030
♪Every day, every night, never tired♪

535
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:46,820
♪By your side♪

