00:25:17,340 --> 00:25:18,560
Hold on a second.

541
00:25:19,220 --> 00:25:22,740
Three, two, one, done.

542
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:23,880
- Thank you.
- Done?

543
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,820
Duoduo, you take our photo.

