00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:39,990
One, two, three.

547
00:25:44,300 --> 00:25:45,540
Perfect.

548
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:46,760
- Check it out.
- Hello.

549
00:25:47,660 --> 00:25:49,980
May I ask how to contact

550
00:25:49,980 --> 00:25:51,300
the artist of this painting?

551
00:25:52,340 --> 00:25:53,860
Why do you want

552
00:25:53,860 --> 00:25:54,940
to contact the artist?

553
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:57,420
I love this painting

554
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,780
of the beach volleyball girls.

555
00:25:59,340 --> 00:26:00,620
I want to buy it.

556
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,060
Buy it?

557
00:26:02,340 --> 00:26:03,180
Yes.

558
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:05,380
I think you look

559
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:07,420
