566
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:20,900
I see.

567
00:26:22,260 --> 00:26:24,180
Sorry, but our paintings are not for sale.

568
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,860
Shao Nian, you're here.

569
00:26:25,860 --> 00:26:26,820
The display is for me.

570
00:26:26,820 --> 00:26:28,140
How could I not come?

571
00:26:28,140 --> 00:26:29,260
You're the artist, right?

572
00:26:29,260 --> 00:26:31,020
- Yes.
