573
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:32,980
I can pay a high price

574
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:34,100
for this painting.

575
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,900
Thank you very much for liking my painting,

576
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:37,180
but sorry,

577
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,980
